{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, Badea and Popescu (2022) used a hybrid approach to mitigate rogue review behavior, whether due to laziness, malevolence, retaliation or dishonesty.",
    "A mechanism was proposed combining automatic labeling of suspicious reviews with manual analysis of content by the teacher.",
    "In addition, dedicated prompts were displayed to the students, providing specific recommendations for revising potentially rogue reviews.",
    "The results of a pilot study were reported.",
    "This area had 19 papers (24%)."
  ]
}